const sqlRouter = {
  route: null,
  name: null,
  title: '数据库',
  type: 'folder',
  icon: 'iconfont icon-database',
  filePath: 'view/sql/',
  order: null,
  inNav: true,
  children: [
    {
      name: 'manage',
      title: '数据库管理',
      type: 'view',
      icon: 'iconfont icon-database',
      route: '/sql/manage',
      filePath: 'view/sql/database-manage.vue',
      permission: ['数据库查询'],
      inNav: true,
    }, {
      name: 'sql-case',
      title: 'SQL脚本',
      type: 'view',
      icon: 'iconfont icon-start',
      route: '/sql/case',
      filePath: 'view/sql/sql-case-list.vue',
      inNav: true,
    }, {
      name: 'batch-execute',
      title: 'SQL批量执行',
      type: 'view',
      icon: 'iconfont icon-start',
      route: '/sql/batch',
      filePath: 'view/sql/batch-execute.vue',
      inNav: true,
    },
  ],
}

export default sqlRouter
